CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

December 3, 2013

[Cite as 12/03/2013 Case Announcements, 2013-Ohio-5283.]

*1419MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

2013-0332. State v. Johnson.

Butler App. No. CA2011-11-212. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Butler County.

Upon consideration of appellee’s motion to reschedule oral argument, it is ordered by the court that the motion is denied.
